<% text_for :title do %>
  Will you be going to a red list country in the 10 days before you return to England?
<% end %>

<% govspeak_for :body do %>
  <%= render "govuk_publishing_components/components/details", {
    title: "Why we’re asking this question:"
  } do %>
    You've told us you’re going to a country on the travel red list.
    Different rules apply if you’ve been in a red list country in the 10 days before you return to England.
  <% end %>

  These are the red list countries you said you're going to:

 <% calculator.red_list_country_titles.each do |country| %>
   - <%= country %>
 <% end %>
<% end %>

<% options(
  "yes": "Yes, I’m going to a red list country in the 10 days before I return to England",
  "no": "No, I’m not going to a red list country in the 10 days before I return to England",
) %>
